summary: A Khajiit follower based off a cat of mine. Have a cat friend wherever you go!
descriptionHtml: So I'm new to the modding scene. I made an account this morning so I could put my mods up here. Dusty is a cat I own and we're super tight, so why not put him into one of my favorite video games? Anyways, you can find him in Rorikstead, hanging out with the cows.
author: Muffinmeister
